HEADWORD: Scauper
<hw>Scaup"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Scalper</er>.]</ety> <def>A tool with a semicircular edge, -- used
by engravers to clear away the spaces between the lines of an
engraving.</def> <rj><au>Fairholt.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

